comment: After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court of a 3 point field goal by Bosh (MIA) was confirmed.
Chandler (PHO) sets the screen on Dragic (MIA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Booker (PHO) jumps in the air towards Wade (MIA) and makes body to body contact that affects Wade's jump shot attempt.
Knight (PHO) commits a take foul on Wade (MIA).
Bosh (MIA) makes contact with Leuer (PHO) that affects his RSBQ.
Dragic (MIA) makes body to body contact with Booker (PHO) that affects his ability to use the screen and take the hand-off.
Wade (MIA) moves his pivot foot as he attempts to avoid the trap.
